131:**Amazon DynamoDB for template storage and versioning.** Stores the current and proposed templates per provider, with version history. Supports the review workflow (proposed vs. approved vs. active states) and rollback if a new template underperforms. For multi-department deployments, scope access using IAM condition keys (`dynamodb:LeadingKeys`) so that each department can only read and modify its own providers' templates.
